# Course Category List in Admin Dashboard

## Admin Page Depiction

This field would display a table containing the list of Course Categories. Here are the table columns that would be shown in the page:

- Course Category title
- Course Category slug
- Course Category description
- Number of courses assigned to the category
- Action button to edit
- Action to assign courses
- Action button to unpublish
- Action button to delete

